trans-unit.source: Base type for <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleExpressionCondition"></xref> and any custom conditions created by users.
trans-unit.target: Bastypen för <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleExpressionCondition"> </xref> och eventuella anpassade villkor som skapats av användare.

trans-unit.source: When implemented in a derived class, initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Implementeras i en härledd klass initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, creates a deep copy of the current <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: När åsidosätts i en härledd klass, skapar du en djup kopia av aktuellt <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref> that is identical to this instance
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref> som är identisk med den här instansen

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, evaluates the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: När åsidosätts i en härledd klass, utvärderas den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The runtime context the rule is running in.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to show that the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref> evaluated to <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>ska visas som den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref> utvärderades till <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets the dependencies for the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: När åsidosätts i en härledd klass hämtar beroendena för den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation"></xref> that was used previously in a call to <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleAction.Validate*>.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation"> </xref> som har använts tidigare i ett anrop till <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleAction.Validate*>.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleAction.Validate*>

trans-unit.source: A list of symbols that represent entities read by the condition.
trans-unit.target: En lista över symboler som representerar enheter läses av villkoret.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger namnet på den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Called when all properties have been given values.
trans-unit.target: Anropas när värden har angetts till alla egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: After this call, no properties can be modified.
trans-unit.target: Inga egenskaper kan inte ändras efter det här anropet.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, verifies that the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref> is configured correctly and has no errors.
trans-unit.target: När åsidosätts i en härledd klass, verifierar du att den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref> är korrekt konfigurerad och inte finns några fel.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition> contains errors (the `Validate` method returns `false`), then <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation.Errors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> will contain the list of errors encountered.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition>innehåller fel (den `Validate` metoden returnerar `false`), sedan <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation.Errors%2A?displayProperty=fullName>innehåller en lista över fel uppstod.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation.Errors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition>

trans-unit.source: The instance of <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation"></xref> that is used to manage the validation of rules and rule conditions.
trans-unit.target: Instansen av <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation"> </xref> som används för att hantera valideringen av regler och regelvillkor.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to show that the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"></xref> has no errors; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>ska visas som den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleCondition"> </xref> inte finns några fel, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
